'''氟化銨'''是一種白色的[[晶體|晶體]]，[[分子式|分子式]]為NH<sub>4</sub>F，易潮解，受热或遇热水分解为[[氨|氨]]与[[氟化氢|氟化氢]]。能腐蚀[[玻璃|玻璃]]。氟化铵可通过[[氢氟酸|氢氟酸]]和[[氨水|氨水]]中和后浓缩结晶製得。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chemyq.com/xz/xz1/252qvsuf.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2008-03-15 |archive-date=2019-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605103546/http://www.chemyq.com/xz/xz1/252qvsuf.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>
::NH<sub>3</sub>.H<sub>2</sub>O + HF → NH<sub>4</sub>F + H<sub>2</sub>O

和所有氟化物一样，氟化铵有中等毒性。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Fluoride Toxicity - an overview {{!}} ScienceDirect Topics|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/pharmacology-toxicology-and-pharmaceutical-science/fluoride-toxicity|access-date=2020-12-16|website=www.sciencedirect.com|archive-date=2021-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211022103207/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/pharmacology-toxicology-and-pharmaceutical-science/fluoride-toxicity|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==晶体结构==
氟化铵是[[纤维锌矿|纤维锌矿]]结构的。在阴离子和阳离子之间有着 N−H···F [[氢键|氢键]]。<ref>A. F. Wells, ''Structural Inorganic Chemistry'', 5th ed., Oxford University Press, Oxford, UK, 1984.</ref>这种结构与[[冰|冰]]非常相似，而氟化铵也是唯一一种可以和冰形成混合晶体的化合物。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Brill|first=R.|author2=Zaromb, S.|title=Mixed Crystals of Ice and Ammonium Fluoride|journal=Nature|volume=173|issue=4398|pages=316–317|doi=10.1038/173316a0}}</ref>

==用处==
氟化铵可用于保存木材，作为防蛀剂，印刷和染[[布|布]]，并作为在[[啤酒厂|啤酒厂]]的[[消毒药水|消毒药水]]。<ref name=Aigueperse>{{Cite book|first = Jean|last = Aigueperse|author2=Paul Mollard |author3=Didier Devilliers |author4=Marius Chemla |author5=Robert Faron |author6=Renée Romano |author7=Jean Pierre Cuer |contribution = Fluorine Compounds, Inorganic|editor-last = Ullmann|title = Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry|year = 2005|publisher = Wiley-VCH|place = Weinheim|doi = 10.1002/14356007.a11_307}}</ref>

